.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, prince, davidoff, dannemann
1. the montecristo-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the prince-smoker##2
2. the prince-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | davidoff | montecristo | prince | dannemann |

 